<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF208-018-350  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 018 350.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>DEC Professional  Oct 1989 v8 n11 p24(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>The search for text and image; Excalibur Technologies' Savvyneural network speeds text and image retrieval. (Software Review)(evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Birkhead, Evan.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Excalibur Technologies Corp (Albuquerque, NM) offers two neuralnetwork programs, Savvy/TRS (text-retrieval system) and Savvy/VRS(visual-recognition system) that use pattern recognition forsearch and retrieval of text and images.andP;  The programs can run ascallable C software functions.andP;  The neural network operationexpands a pattern-recognition database through the learning of newpatterns in search query processing.andP;  Queried patterns arecompared to those in the database, with candidate results reportedin a numerical hierarchy.andP;  Both programs include PixTex, anintegrated text and vision system for inputting, storing, andretrieving scanned documents.andP;  Savvy/TRS is $12,000 to $44,000,depending on the target Digital Equipment Corp VAX system.andO;Savvy/VRS, which searches input video images, is $45,000 for adevelopment system.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Excalibur Technologies Corp. (products).andO;Product:   Savvy/VRS (Computer program)Savvy/TRS (Computer program).andO;Topic:     EvaluationSearchingSoftware PackagesPattern Recognition.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>